Don't get caught by the red fog.

319
00:36:57,380 --> 00:36:58,970
Fan Lao!

320
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:19,050
You... your Fight Qi.

321
00:38:19,730 --> 00:38:21,220
Don't forget...

